{"tid":1457844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"驚總果班 遞信 撚做緊乜9","createTime":"2019-08-12T12:23:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T15:31:11.000Z","uid":135867,"like":70,"dislike":228,"uniUserReply":137,"replies":[{"pid":"33be2b1db442b474063adb80a9485b23726832eb","tid":1457844,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪以為啲犬會睇"},{"pid":"4bf7fddbad03bf317aaeddac8a35c89b333086ec","tid":1457844,"uid":2455,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:23:46.000Z","msg":"和理非"},{"pid":"90ff13acaf1c52ece3961277b964d750b74135d0","tid":1457844,"uid":9431,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:23:46.000Z","msg":"有冇人知封信寫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6290837750d7308a5b2df8d8dac428377745f3b4","tid":1457844,"uid":135867,"like":8,"dislike":8,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:23:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後而家散了"},{"pid":"1049716d17e0aa3afc9334849c686f25b06a44d1","tid":1457844,"uid":33868,"like":218,"dislike":0,"score":218,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:23:53.000Z","msg":"各有各做<br />\n呢班係社工咪做番社工既野"},{"pid":"3f5590ac0448206d62e2d9081aa7472900b9be6a","tid":1457844,"uid":135867,"like":5,"dislike":62,"score":-57,"quote":{"pid":"4bf7fddbad03bf317aaeddac8a35c89b333086ec","tid":1457844,"uid":2455,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:23:46.000Z","msg":"和理非"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:24:13.000Z","msg":"仲衰過和理非"},{"pid":"7a19f34d6c854cd7ff3cea7e08ee7b5c52a73dcd","tid":1457844,"uid":17244,"like":127,"dislike":0,"score":127,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:25:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三毛分化撚</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力</span></span></ins></strong>"},{"pid":"4c1f772d94b14cfaa1870f7988c7180918e8f402","tid":1457844,"uid":254361,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:25:57.000Z","msg":"借位講幾句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我求下各位巴打絲打<br />\n用下個腦諗嘢<br />\n留又好，唔留又好請交給在場人士去決定<br />\n你哋唔好喺度發文喺度煽動<br />\n佢地成功分化我地了啦<br />\n<br />\n和理非非會驚好多野係正常<br />\n（唔驚又有行動力做左勇武）<br />\n但係但係呢到我有幾句野想講<br />\n<br />\n直面面對「恐怖」，知道它的「傷害」<br />\n理解會造成的「後果」，站起來、面對它<br />\n這才是「勇氣」，這才是「抗爭」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有沒有看過周星馳的電影「少林足球」<br />\n當然還有其他優秀的電影，如「讓子彈飛一會」等等<br />\n<br />\n「少林足球」里而的大反派說了這麼幾句 <br />\n<br />\n強雄：「我是打人,怎麼樣? 我要把你全隊的人打得像你一樣殘廢、殘廢、殘廢... 跟我鬥?」<br />\n強雄：「還有球證、旁證加上主辦、協辦所有的單位，全部都是我的人，怎麼和我鬥?」<br />\n<br />\n係呀點鬥呀，只剩下咩可以去鬥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加油呀，香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後這再講返幾句名言<br />\n曼德拉語錄:<br />\n如果天空是黑暗的，那就摸黑生存;<br />\n如果發出聲音是危險的，那就保持沉默;<br />\n如果自覺無力發光，那就蜷伏於牆角。<br />\n但是，不要習慣了黑暗就為黑暗辯護;<br />\n也不要為自己的苟且而得意;<br />\n不要嘲諷那些比自己更勇敢的人。<br />\n我們可以卑微如塵土，但不可扭曲如蛆蟲。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;曼德拉《漫漫人生路》"},{"pid":"ae789f43c8356e245bce116cdc3c33f41213f8f2","tid":1457844,"uid":109780,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:26:08.000Z","msg":"分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad172643ed927a70b2b95b8fa3bd02951fe5049","tid":1457844,"uid":36702,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:26:13.000Z","msg":"雖然大家都知黑警唔識字<br />\n<br />\n亦都係香港入面最低賤嘅有機生命體<br />\n<br />\n不過佢地遞下信  等班狗調動下人手  唔洗勞氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da1a7e800c3935b8531a809ea5b310060d98984","tid":1457844,"uid":67816,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:27:05.000Z","msg":"各有各做姐 社福界係咁架啦"},{"pid":"1f7e49c3332926e083ea8c3b240e8776fa12e7f5","tid":1457844,"uid":39215,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:27:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分化！！！</span>"},{"pid":"abe3a0ff3caf606e8e5d0ecfe3042abe38a20b4b","tid":1457844,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:27:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">612 721 811<br />\n心態改變命運<br />\n人數決定一切<br />\n<br />\n你 班 仆 街 幾 時 先 肯 無 限 期 四 罷？？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1450867\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1450867</a><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"64d70666307bc07aaf4d5a8dc8d451d3038f3c62","tid":1457844,"uid":276968,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:27:47.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山"},{"pid":"837c72b88cb0f0ee3c946986883d3fa30da0e893","tid":1457844,"uid":142903,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:27:59.000Z","msg":"社工係咁架啦"},{"pid":"39be727c9805164f0a15a5ef961e3e04d1515dfb","tid":1457844,"uid":2781,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:29:33.000Z","msg":"好多分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7006038f39f35a4f35eeedd52eb5fc5a0651732a","tid":1457844,"uid":135867,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:30:43.000Z","msg":"我驚佢哋送頭呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁都屌我分化"},{"pid":"0af7e8acfc37962e433cb8501d854d7f70aed829","tid":1457844,"uid":265171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:30:47.000Z","msg":"各有各做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7154b1e3687c417ef20b3abf95e3be8